"times, and supplier reliability to ensure quality and timely delivery."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເລືອກຜູ້ສະໜອງທີ່ເໝາະສົມ</strong> ໂດຍການປຽບທຽບລາຄາ, ເວລາສົ່ງເຄື່ອງ, ແລະ ຄວາມໜ້າເຊື່"
"ອຖື ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນຄຸນນະພາບ ແລະ ການສົ່ງມອບທີ່ຕົງເວລາ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Send a Request for Quotation (RFQ)</strong> to suppliers directly "
"from Odoo or confirm the order when you've made your choice."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສົ່ງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ (RFQ)</strong> ຫາຜູ້ສະໜອງໂດຍກົງຈາກ Odoo ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນການສັ່ງຊື້ເມື່ອທ່ານເ"
"ລືອກໄດ້ແລ້ວ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Send them to participants,</strong> staff, and sponsors after the "
"event."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສົ່ງໃຫ້ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມ,</strong> ພະນັກງານ, ແລະ ຜູ້ອຸປະຖຳ ຫຼັງຈົບກິດຈະກຳ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Set Reordering Rules</strong> by defining minimum and maximum stock "
"levels. Example: Keep at least 200 gels in stock, and replenish up to 500 "
"when you drop below the threshold."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕັ້ງກົດການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນ</strong> ໂດຍກຳນົດລະດັບສິນຄ້າຕໍ່າສຸດ ແລະ ສູງສຸດ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ເກັບເຈວພະລັງ"
"ງານໄວ້ຢ່າງໜ້ອຍ 200 ອັນ, ແລະ ຕື່ມໃຫ້ຮອດ 500 ອັນ ເມື່ອເຄື່ອງຫຼຸດລົງຕໍ່າກວ່າກຳນົດ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Set up a project</strong> in the <em>Project</em> app to assign and "
"track tasks such as venue booking, course setup, and sponsor contact."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕັ້ງໂຄງການ</strong> ໃນແອັບ <em>ໂຄງການ</em> ເພື່ອມອບໝາຍ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມວຽກ ເຊັ່ນ ກາ"
"ນຈອງສະຖານທີ່, ການຈັດເສັ້ນທາງ, ແລະ ການຕິດຕໍ່ຜູ້ອຸປະຖຳ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Showcase your value proposition and current sponsors</strong> with "
"logos, testimonials, and success stories. Include a sponsor interest form "
"that, when submitted, automatically creates an opportunity in the CRM. This "
"allows your team to track sponsor activity, follow up effectively, and work "
"toward converting them into long-term partners."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສະແດງຈຸດເດັ່ນ ແລະ ຜູ້ອຸປະຖຳປັດຈຸບັນ</strong> ດ້ວຍໂລໂກ້ ແລະ ເລື່ອງລາວຄວາມສຳເລັດ. ເພີ່ມ"
"ແບບຟອມສຳລັບຜູ້ທີ່ສົນໃຈອຸປະຖຳ ເຊິ່ງຈະສ້າງໂອກາດໃນ CRM ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທີມງານຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ປ່ຽນ"
"ພວກເຂົາໃຫ້ເປັນຄູ່ຮ່ວມງານໄລຍະຍາວ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_1
msgid ""
"<strong>Start &amp; Finish:</strong> Microbrasserie de Maredsous – Abtei "
"Maredsous, Belgium"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຈຸດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ເສັ້ນໄຊ:</strong> Microbrasserie de Maredsous – Abtei "
"Maredsous, Belgium"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Support</strong>: 1 aid station at halfway point"
msgstr "<strong>ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</strong>: ຈຸດບໍລິການ 1 ແຫ່ງ ຢູ່ເຄິ່ງທາງ"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Support</strong>: 2 aid stations (KM 7 and KM 14)"
msgstr "<strong>ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</strong>: ຈຸດບໍລິການ 2 ແຫ່ງ (ກິໂລແມັດທີ 7 ແລະ 14)"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_1
msgid "<strong>Support</strong>: 4 aid stations, positioned every 10 km"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ</strong>: ຈຸດບໍລິການ 4 ແຫ່ງ, ຕັ້ງຢູ່ທຸກໆ 10 ກິໂລແມັດ"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_3
msgid "<strong>Swim. Bike. Run. Embrace the Challenge.</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ລອຍນ້ຳ. ຖີບລົດ. ແລ່ນ. ກຽມຮັບຄຳທ້າທາຍ.</strong>"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_3
msgid ""
"<strong>Swim</strong>: 1.5 km open-water in Lac de Nisramont (wetsuit "
"recommended)"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລອຍນ້ຳ</strong>: 1.5 ກິໂລແມັດ ໃນແຫຼ່ງນ້ຳທຳມະຊາດ Lac de Nisramont (ແນະນຳໃຫ້ໃສ່"
"ຊຸດລອຍນ້ຳແບບເວດຊຸດ)"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:survey.survey,description_done:sport_events.survey_survey_1
msgid "<strong>Thank you for sharing your thoughts!</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຂອບໃຈທີ່ແບ່ງປັນຄຳຄິດເຫັນຂອງທ່ານ!</strong>"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:event.event,description:sport_events.event_event_2
msgid "<strong>Tournament Format</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຮູບແບບການແຂ່ງຂັນ</strong>"

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Track payments</strong> and send reminders for overdue invoices."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕິດຕາມການຊຳລະເງິນ</strong> ແລະ ສົ່ງການແຈ້ງເຕືອນສຳລັບໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້ທີ່ເກີນກຳນົດ."

#. module: sport_events
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sport_events.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Track the order</strong> in <em>Purchase</em> to monitor expected "
